<fest:template xmlns:fest="http://fest.mail.ru">
  <div class="b-page__line">
    <div class="b-page__rule">
      <h3>Idea of the game</h3>
      <div class="b-page__rule-open">
        <label class="btn" for="rule_1">Read</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="rule_1"/>
        <div class="rule__text">
          The purpose of this game is to collect as many coins as possible and
          bring them to your ship. Seek them by fair means or foul.
          Do you like to bravely go into battle, tactfully avoid meetings with enemies,
          and you are a skillful truce envoy?
          It is in your power. The main thing is to catch cherished gold!!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="b-page__rule">
      <h3>Cell fields</h3>
      <div class="b-page__rule-open">
        <label class="btn" for="rule_2">Read</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="rule_2"/>
        <div class="rule__text">
          <div class="page__line">
            <div class="rules">
              <div class="rules__item rules__item_small">
                <ul class="cell-content">
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Coins
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        cannot be brought to the Fortress or some squares,cannot stay on Arrows.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Arrows
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        Choose any offered direction and proceed right away
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Labyrinths
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        a number of moves required for leaving the square is shown on it
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Ice
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        repeat your move in the same direction. you have come on ice
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Trap
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        fall to a hole; rescue your pirate if another pirate comes to the aid.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Gun
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        a Pirate has a pleasant
                        flight directed by the gun tube and lands on water
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rules">
              <div class="rules__item rules__item_small">
                <ul class="cell-content">
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Beacon
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        using it, you can open any 4 closed squares and then it disappears
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Cave
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        every time  you enter the Cave, should choose another one and pass to it
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Earthquake
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        swap over any two opened squares not occupied by Items or players
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Jungle
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        any number of players and their pirates can be on this square
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Balloon
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        fly to the ship, and Items you have do the same.
                        Repeated entering
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Wheelbarrow
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        can transport any 2 items, cannot enter a fortress or go on closed
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rules">
              <div class="rules__item rules__item_small">
                <ul class="cell-content">
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Horse
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        Horse - do a horse's move as a knight's move in old good chess
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Castle
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        nobody can attack you since walls protect a pirate well.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Rum Cask
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        a pirate who has found a Rum Cask enjoys it and doesn't make the next.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Crocodile
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        a Pirate cannot enter this square and
                        returns to the previous square
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Cannibal
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        Cannibal - after finding the cannibal, a Pirate becomes his dinner
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="cell-content__item">
                    <div class="cell">
                      <img class="cell__img" src="static/img/sq.png"></img>
                      <div class="cell__head">
                        Plane
                      </div>
                      <div class="cell__text">
                        Plane -can send you with Items to any square of the island, both opened
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</fest:template>
